  "title": "Finance Associate",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Financial Modeling & Valuation:</strong> Create, analyze, and audit complex valuation models in Excel (e.g., DCF, LBO, comparable company analysis).</li><li><strong>Transaction Execution:</strong> Manage day-to-day workstreams for M&A and capital raising deals, including due diligence and coordinating with internal/external parties.</li><li><strong>Pitch Materials & Presentations:</strong> Prepare PowerPoint-based pitch books, CIMs (Confidential Information Memoranda), and marketing materials for clients.</li><li><strong>Project Management & Mentorship:</strong> Supervise and review the work of junior analysts, ensuring accuracy and managing timelines for multiple projects.</li><li><strong>Client Interaction:</strong> Participate in client meetings, management interviews, and Q&A sessions. </li></ul>",
